<script type="text/javascript">
function togPhase(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + n);
	e.style.display = e.style.display == 'none' ? 'block' : 'none';
}
function togAllPhases(display) {
	for (var i = 1; i <= 50; i++) {
		var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + i);
		if (!e) break;
		e.style.display = display;
	}
}
function addHint(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phase');
	for (var i = 0; i < e.childNodes.length; i++) {
		e.childNodes[i].selected = e.childNodes[i].value == n ? 'selected' : '';
	}
	e = document.getElementById('text');
	e.focus();
	e.select();
}
</script>

<div class="mm white">
This quest <span class="blue">[<span class="yellow">2252</span>]</span> is called '<span class="yellow">Child's Play: The Brave Little Tailor</span>',<br/>
for Adventurers levels <span class="yellow">60</span> to <span class="yellow">120</span>.<br />


<span class="hg"><a href="/npc/3438">Lord Vashir</a> [<a href="/area/61">The Towne of New Rigel</a>] is the master in charge of this quest.</span><br />

The royal theatre in New Rigel is planning on performing some plays<br />
especially for children.  The plays are all based on popular children's<br />
stories.  I need you to help them recover some of the props they need for<br />
the play "The Brave Little Tailor".<br />

<span class="hy">Upon successful completion of this quest you can receive:</span><br />

<span class="hm">*</span>Up to <span class="yellow">30</span> quest points, <span class="yellow">3</span> practice points, <span class="yellow">9,000</span> experience points,<br/>
&nbsp;<span class="yellow">0</span> build points, <span class="yellow">0</span> piety, and <span class="yellow">2,000</span> gold pieces.<br />


You have <span class="yellow">240</span> minutes remaining to complete this quest.<br />

Child's Play: The Brave Little Tailor consists of:<br />


